<br>
My opinion is I went on raids for three reasons:<br>
<br>
1) First time there. Once there, no desire to go back unless I liked it.<br>
<br>
2) Help friends (epics, etc ~ most common reason)<br>
<br>
3) Loot.  Most of us were there for the loot.  It's a fact most don't like to admit.  The cheers that occur when the plate bp drops for the next in line but the bickering among some that they should get it.  I have heard it.  Congratulations on 100 plus NTOV raids.  There are firsts.  You need better gear to move on.  Many have excellent gear on this server to compete with others in BoT.<br>
<br>
