<br>
As for this public display of love, while some may say it is respect of what others are doing in Pixel World, for me it comes off as sucking up.  Get to 60 and apply.  <br>
<br>
Finally, if it isn't about the loot. If it truly isn't about the loot!!!  Then once your guild members don't need a piece of armor, a weapon or a spell, instead of selling it....pass it on......Hey, it's not about the loot.<br>
<br>
Well, slash away but my opinion won't change after almost 3 years in game (off and on).<br>
<br>
Have fun in GAME!<br>
<br>
Grumpy old Graves<br>
